                "SIBAR",
                "CSICR"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "  MEDLEY set-up",
                " The light charged particles, produced in the reaction",
                " target, were detected by means of eight three-detector",
                " telescopes, each composed of two silicon detectors and",
                " a CsI(Tl)-crystal. The silicon detectors are thin for",
                " the delta-E1 detectors of 50-60 um  and more",
                " thick for the delta-E2 400-500 um.",
                " The material of E-detectors is CsI(Tl) scintillator",
                " crystal, 5.0 cm long, consisting of a cylindrical and",
                " a conical part.",
                " An Am-241 alpha-source, introduced in the center of",
                " the MEDLEY chamber, was used to obtain data for the",
                " energy calibration of the delta-E detectors."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                " Target assembly consists of two targets of 238U-F4,",
